## Profile Delete

delete-q = A gba bɔri ni a suhi soli ka kɔko' shɛŋa a ni n yaagi la nyahi, bee a suhu yuya ni di m-be Common Voice kpanjɔɣu la puuni?
keep = Gbubibu
remove = Yihima
keep-info = A lɔŋ din sɔɣi ŋɔ nyɛla din na yɛn be Common Voice dataset ŋɔ ni. Di yi kuli niŋ ka a nyahi a "profile" a ku tooi lahi suhi ni bɛ yihi a kukoli dataset ŋɔ ni.
remove-info = Ti ni labi vihi a ni suhi ni di yihimi a kukoli dataset ŋɔ ni maa. Di yi niŋ ka a suhigu ŋɔ deei, ti ni boli ban pun downloadi dataset ŋɔ ka suhi ba ni bɛ yihimi a kukoli ŋɔ gba.
profile-form-delete = Nyahimi maŋmaŋa lahibali jia
